data.description: Your WATERFRONT dream home is here! The fantastic curb appeal boasts a circular driveway surrounded by mature landscaping and a huge, covered, stamped concrete front porch! If you love the front of the home, check out the back! The oversized boat dock was rebuilt in 2021 with a 10,000lb boat lift, with water & electric so you can store your boats with ease in your own backyard! This one-story home is a boater’s dream with 78’ of canal frontage and is situated just minutes from Tampa Bay! Not only do you have the best view to relax and enjoy, you have your own solar heated, caged swimming pool (recently rescreened) and new fire pit area for days that you are looking to have some fun at home! Part of the patio is enclosed with a wall of impact sliders leading out to the pool, so you have the option to open up the area or close it off! Featuring incredible natural light, an ideal split floor plan with functionality in mind; this 3+ bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a must-see! Sellers have installed owned solar panels to keep your electric bill ridiculously low! Once inside you will discover a bright and airy layout with neutral color paint throughout all the living areas, ready to welcome all your furnishings and decor! Upgrades include a newer A/C from May 2021 with a 10-year warranty, a newer intercom system that works throughout the home, upgraded bathrooms, and MORE! The formal living and dining room combination creates the perfect space for entertaining guests, especially with the sliding glass door leading to the patio! The heart of the home is the kitchen! This room is so functional with an abundance of rich wood cabinets with under mount lighting, granite counters with breakfast bar seating that extends to the patio through a sliding window so you can enjoy your meals inside or out! The spacious breakfast nook offers its own exit to the lanai for your everyday meals and flows right into the family room! Such great memories are meant to be made in this room, there is plenty of space for the entire family to enjoy each other! The master suite is tucked away on one side of the home with his and her closets, upgraded en-suite with ceramic tile set at the diagonal, dual sinks, vanity lighting, and a walk-in shower! On the other side of the home are two additional bedrooms sharing a second full bathroom and a cozy office or 4th bedroom, perfect for working from home or e-learning! Between the beautiful upgrades and backyard paradise, this home is sure to check off all of your boxes!
